# 📊 DapperKaggle Dashboard Project

A large-scale e-commerce analytics and management dashboard project developed using ASP.NET Core MVC, Dapper and SQL Server.

This project focuses on high-performance SQL operations, dashboard reporting systems, search, filtering, server-side pagination and product CRUD operations.

---


# 🚀 About The Project

DapperKaggle is a dashboard-based management system developed using a Kaggle e-commerce dataset.

Main goals of the project:

- Learning Dapper architecture
- Working with large-scale datasets
- Building dashboard and reporting systems
- Creating search and filtering structures
- Implementing server-side pagination
- Developing a layered architecture

---

# 📦 Dataset Information

A large-scale Kaggle e-commerce dataset was used in this project.

The dataset contains:

- 👥 1,997,810 Customers
- 📦 994,705 Products
- 🛒 1,000,123 Orders
- ⭐ 1,000,123 Reviews
- 📋 1,000,123 Order Items
- 🗂️ 1,000,123 Ecommerce Records

Dashboard analytics, filtering, search and server-side pagination systems were developed on top of this large dataset.

