# 📄 Pagination System

Custom server-side pagination was implemented for Orders and Products pages.

All records are not loaded at once. SQL Server `OFFSET` and `FETCH NEXT` were used to retrieve only the required page data.

```sql
OFFSET @skip ROWS FETCH NEXT @take ROWS ONLY
```

This approach improves performance for large datasets.

